THE PUBLIC LIBRARY MISSION STATEMENT AND ITS IMPERATIVES FOR SERVICE.
     
WORK PREPARED BY THE PUBLIC LIBRARY ASSOCIATION GOALS, GUIDELINES, AND
STANDARDS COMMITTEE. INTERIM STATEMENT, PRODUCED AS A BRIDGE TO THE NEW AND
LONG-DESIRED APPROACH TO LIBRARY STANDARDS. PRESENTS A STATEMENT ON THE
PRESENT US PUBLIC LIBRARY SITUATION, DETAILS OF NEEDED RESPONSES TO SOCIAL
CHANGE AND IMPERATIVES FOR PUBLIC LIBRARY SERVICES.
